high_descs: Turn around and walk to the knife on the far counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn to your left and walk to the lettuce to the left of the sink.
Slice the lettuce on the counter.
Move slightly to your left and turn so the counter with the lettuce is on your left side.
Place the knife on the counter in front of the lettuce.
Move to stand directly in front of the lettuce and the knife.
Pick up the left end of the lettuce.
Turn to your right and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the lettuce slice to the left of the potato on the top shelf, close the door; after cooling, open the door, pick up the lettuce slice, close the door.
Turn to your left and walk to the sink.
Place the lettuce slice on the counter directly in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Slice a head of lettuce, chill a slice, put the slice in front of the sink

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter to the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk past the sink, then turn to the counter on your right.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn to your right.
Place the knife on the edge of the counter, in front of the lettuce.
Turn to your left, back to the lettuce.
Pick up one of the lettuce slices.
Turn around and walk to the stove, then turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Place the lettuce slice on the shelf to the left of the tomato, wait a moment for the lettuce to chill, then remove the lettuce from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the sink to your right.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right then head to the counter on the right beside the fridge
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left head to the left side of the sink counter
Slice the cabbage
Turn left then, turn right face the other side of the counter
Place the knife of the edge of the counter
Walk forward then turn left
Pick up a slice of cabbage
Turn right then head to the frigde
Open fridge put in and out the slice cabbage
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the slice of cabbage in front of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice cabbage in front of the sink
